plot: Geoff insists to join Alf when the SES (emergency volunteers corps) is mobilized to search for badly wounded Jai and Annie, but Martin and Miles find them. After an innocent peck on Nicole's cheek makes Trey generally rejected again, more bullying from step-dad drives him to plant his self-made bomb under the bus. Hugo takes Martha on a short trip, to escape Colleen's nagging.   Written by  KGF Vissers
